## README

## Setup 
1. Download Visual Studio Community Version
https://www.visualstudio.com/en-us/products/visual-studio-community-vs.aspx

2. To continue using a free license, you must sign up for a Microsoft VS account

3. Sign up for Bitbucket - have an admin add you to the Zeebs project

4. Download TortoiseHg or an equivalent mercurial SVN program 

5. Clone the project into your local


## Starting the app
1. Open zeebs.sln in Visual Studio

2. Copy the files in zeebs/lib into zeebs/bin/Debug

3. In zeebs/bin/Debug/save replace MainConfig with: (you may need to run the program first to produce this file)

{
  "CurrentMusic": "",
  "MaxPlayers": "500",
  "AdminUser": "Tankooni",
  "OverrideBotUser": "",
  "OverrideOauth": "",
  "Channel": "#tankooni",
  "PreventBotTalking": "false",
  "DefaultBody": "ZeebSmall",
  "IsDebug": "true",
  "IsOfflineMode": "false",
  "BackgroundColor": "#00FF00",
  "UseBackgroundImage": "true",
  "ShowLeaderBoard": "true"
}

Tweaking settings as you wish. The current settings point to www.twitch.tv/tankooni

4. Run the program on Visual Studio!